ingredients: ["2 c. cooked lentils", "1/4 c. chopped cooked carrots", "1/4 c. green onions", "1 Tbsp. butter", "1/2 tsp. salt", "1/2 tsp. pepper", "1 c. tomato juice", "2 c. lentil juice (the water that lentils are cooked in)", "1/2 c. parsley, finely chopped"]
directions: ["Mix all ingredients together; heat to boiling.", "Add one tablespoon butter; salt and pepper to taste.", "Serve hot."]

title: Sourdough Bread Or Cinnamon Rolls
ingredients: ["6 c. bread flour", "1 c. sugar", "3 Tbsp. potato flakes", "1/2 c. vegetable oil", "1 Tbsp. salt", "2 1/2 c. hot water", "1 c. starter", "cinnamon butter or margarine to taste"]
directions: ["Take 1 cup of starter from a friend.", "Add 1/2 cup sugar, potato flakes and 1 cup hot water.", "Leave out 8 to 12 hours.", "Take 1 cup of starter that has been out (put other back in refrigerator for 3 to 5 days).", "Add 1/2 cup of sugar, vegetable oil, salt and 1 1/2 cups hot water.", "Mix and gradually add bread flour.", "Make dough; let rise 8 to 12 hours.", "Make into loaves or rolls.", "(Press flat and sprinkle with sugar, cinnamon and chips of butter.", "Roll up and cut.)", "Let rise 8 to 12 hours.", "Bake at 325\u00b0 for 20 to 25 minutes."]
